Email
Please complete the form below to send a message to an Ivy client service representative. Maintaining your confidential information is important to us, and accordingly, all information contained within this message will be encrypted as a means of securing the information you provide. Because all information you send within this message will remain confidential, you may include personal or account information. However, we cannot provide personal account information in an e-mail response without compromising your privacy.
We will make every effort to respond to you within two business days of receipt of your message. While we read all messages, we generally respond only to questions. If you send us a suggestion or general comment, you may not receive a response. At this time, we cannot respond to or execute any transaction-related e-mail. If you are a current shareholder and wish to buy, sell or exchange shares, contact your financial advisor or call a client service representative (1-800-777-6472) for assistance. As always, we recommend that you contact your financial advisor before adjusting your portfolio.
